					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Both of those machines are framebuffer based, without any tiles and whatnot (except C64 in its character modes). Framebuffer sits in main memory that is shared by CPU, and accessible as normal RAM to the CPU.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.tmeeco.eu">http://www.tmeeco.eu</a><!-- m --></div>
